---
// Problem section - dark background with stats
---

<section id="problem" class="section-dark py-24 lg:py-32 px-6 lg:px-10">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto relative z-10">
    <div class="text-center mb-16 reveal">
      <span
        class="inline-block text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest mb-4"
        style="color: var(--color-gold);"
      >
        The Problem
      </span>
      <h2 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-semibold" style="color: var(--color-cream);">
        Europe Is Falling Behind.<br />Your Savings Shouldn't.
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <div
        class="reveal rounded-2xl p-8 backdrop-blur-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:translate-y-[-5px]"
        style="background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05); border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);"
      >
        <div class="font-display text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold leading-none mb-4" style="color: var(--color-coral);">
          0.9%
        </div>
        <div class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2" style="color: var(--color-cream);">
          EU Productivity Growth
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);">
          EU labor productivity grew just 0.9% since 2019, while the US grew 6.7%.
        </p>
        <p class="text-xs mt-4" style="color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);">
          ECB Economic Bulletin 2024
        </p>
      </div>

      <div
        class="reveal rounded-2xl p-8 backdrop-blur-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:translate-y-[-5px]"
        style="background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05); border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);"
      >
        <div class="font-display text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold leading-none mb-4" style="color: var(--color-coral);">
          30%
        </div>
        <div class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2" style="color: var(--color-cream);">
          Income Gap
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);">
          EU per capita income is now 30% below US levels and the gap is widening.
        </p>
        <p class="text-xs mt-4" style="color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);">
          IMF "Europe's Choice" 2024
        </p>
      </div>

      <div
        class="reveal rounded-2xl p-8 backdrop-blur-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:translate-y-[-5px]"
        style="background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05); border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);"
      >
        <div class="font-display text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold leading-none mb-4" style="color: var(--color-coral);">
          âˆž
        </div>
        <div class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2" style="color: var(--color-cream);">
          AI Wealth Gap
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);">
          AI adoption consistently increases wealth inequality. Capital owners benefit disproportionately.
        </p>
        <p class="text-xs mt-4" style="color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);">
          IMF Working Paper 2025
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
